Ask HN: Rate your current Project Mngmt tool
text:
Some of the PM tools we used started to be very simple and easy to use, but their UX and features got complicated eventually.

How happy are you with your current PM tool? What are the pain points it's not currently addressing?

We are starting a new project with 30 developers to work on, and we will decide on which PM tool we should use. Your feedback is highly appreciated.
